<div class=\"post-item-right\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"post_details\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"post-title-alt\"><a\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\thref=\"https:\/\/nacom.org\/thematic-areas\/pollution-control\/\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\ttitle=\"Pollution Control\">Pollution Control<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/h2>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Pollution is a serious problem to the development and health of the Bangladeshi people. From Air pollution alone, every year in Bangladesh more that 1.5 million people die. NACOM also thrives for pollution control especially for Air Pollution. NACOM engage with different stakeholders to evaluate, investigate and consult regarding the&hellip;<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/nacom.org\/thematic-areas\/pollution-control\/\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t   class=\"kc-post-2-button\">Details <i\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"fa fa-angle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"kc-list-item-2\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"post-item-left\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"post_details\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"post-title-alt\"><a\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\thref=\"https:\/\/nacom.org\/thematic-areas\/capacity-building-and-awareness\/\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\ttitle=\"Capacity Building and Awareness\">Capacity Building and Awareness<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Capacity building of the different stakeholders is central to the successful project implementation and sustainability of a project. NACOM is highly capable of designing crafted training framework for different stakeholders based on their needs and capacity. Also NACOM is highly capable of raising awareness among the local communities regarding different&hellip;<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/nacom.org\/thematic-areas\/capacity-building-and-